| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-0781 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3a765df5-1a61-54e9-9ee2-b5de5f57a60a"
